- **Script de Prueba:**  
  ```python  
  # locustfile.py  
  from locust import HttpUser, task, between  

  class UserBehavior(HttpUser):  
      wait_time = between(1, 5)  

      @task  
      def generate_content(self):  
          self.client.post("/api/generate", json={"prompt": "prueba"})  

      @task  
      def mint_nft(self):  
          self.client.post("/api/nft/mint")  
  ```  

