    - `feature-requests` (votaci√≥n p√∫blica).  
  - **Script de Anal√≠tica:**  
    ```python  
    # analyze_feedback.py  
    from github import Github  
    g = Github("token")  
    repo = g.get_repo("ttbt2/ttbt2")  
    bugs = repo.get_issues(labels=["bug"])  
    for bug in bugs:  
        if bug.comments < 5:  
            bug.add_labels("needs-triage")  
    ```  

