#### **2. Script de Despliegue de NFTs de Voz**  
```yaml  
# k8s/audio_nft.yaml  
apiVersion: apps/v1  
kind: Deployment  
metadata:  
  name: ttbt2-audio-nft  
spec:  
  replicas: 2  
  selector:  
    matchLabels:  
      app: audio-nft  
  template:  
    spec:  
      containers:  
      - name: audio-nft  
        image: ttbt2-audio-nft:latest  
        ports:  
        - containerPort: 5003  
        env:  
        - name: OPENAI_API_KEY  
          valueFrom:  
            secretKeyRef:  
              name: openai-credentials  
              key: API_KEY  
```  

