      metadata:  
        labels:  
          app: ttbt2-beta  
      spec:  
        containers:  
        - name: ttbt2-beta  
          image: ttbt2:beta  
          ports:  
          - containerPort: 5000  
  ```  

- **CDN de Contenido Est√°tico:**  
  ```bash  
